         <div type="translation" source="#chaniotis2012">
            <p>The sarcophagus and the niche under it and the place, on which the sarcophagus and the niche are standing, belong to
               Marcus Aurelius ---, son of Adrastos, son of Kallippos, son of Polydeukes.</p>
         </div>
         <div type="translation" source="#iaph2007">
            <p>The sarcophagus and the burial niche lying below and the place on which the sarcophagus and the niche are located belong to Marcus Aurelius [ . . . .]
               son of Adrastos son of Kallippos son of Polydeukes.</p>
         </div>
